**********************************************************
****** DABC plugin for hadaq 
****** (originally HADES collaboration DAQ and data format)
*        Joern Adamczewski-Musch, j.adamczewski@gsi.de
* Development Version 0.01 - 06-Jun-2012
   : design of classes and first successful compilation

* Components:
   * HldFile - input and output to hld file format
   * HldInput - read hadtu format from file
   * HldOutput- write hadtu format to file
   * UdpDataSocket - receive hadtu packets from trb frontend (single stream).
   * MbsTransmitterModule - wrap hadtu format into mbs event container
                            output is mbs server or lmd file.
                            this format is used in mbs combiner and go4 unpacker 
   * CombinerModule - do eventbuilding of hadtu format from several data streams.
                      output is full event in hadtu format. This will be functionality of old daq_evtbuild.
                      
